      <title>kirta 5.2.9 软件分享安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/26/kirta%205.2.9%20%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/26/kirta%205.2.9%20%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Krita 5.2.9是一款功能强大的自由开源数字绘画软件。它由社区驱动开发，针对画师、概念设计师、动画师、漫画师等专业人士以及绘画爱好者的需求设计。该软件拥有友好的用户界面，面板和工具可灵活定制，方便用户根据自己的工作流程进行设置，并能保存为自定义工作区，还支持为常用工具设置快捷键。Krita 5.2.9提供了丰富的功能，如多种笔刷引擎、支持压感等数位板传感器、十多种色彩模型，以及强大的图层管理功能，包括多种类型的图层和蒙版。此外，它的变形工具丰富，能满足从标准变形到高级变形的各种需求。在文件处理方面，Krita 5.2.9能打开甚至Photoshop无法打开的PSD文件，支持HDR和场景参考图像的编辑，还通过相关技术支持实现了全色彩管理。5.2.9版本主要是一个Bug修复版本，对克隆图层、不透明度处理、EXR文件格式等方面进行了关键修复，提高了软件的稳定性和性能。</p><h2>安装教程</h2><p>1.下载完成后，鼠标右击【Krita 5.2.9】压缩包，选择【解压至此处】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-62213 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-24.jpg" width="812" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-24.jpg 812w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-24-768x600.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 812px) 100vw, 812px" title="Krita 5.2.9插图" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图" data-mwl-img-id="62213" mwl-index="0"></p><p>2.找到【Krita-x64-5.2.9-setup】应用程序，右键选择【以管理员身份运行】它</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62214 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-24.jpg" width="812" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-24.jpg 812w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-24-768x600.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 812px) 100vw, 812px" title="Krita 5.2.9插图1" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图1" data-mwl-img-id="62214" mwl-index="1"></p><p>3.点击【OK】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62215 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/3-24.jpg" width="290" height="155" title="Krita 5.2.9插图2" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图2" data-mwl-img-id="62215" mwl-index="2"></p><p>4.点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62216 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/4-24.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图3" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图3" data-mwl-img-id="62216" mwl-index="3"></p><p>5.勾选【我接受】，再点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62217 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/5-23.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图4" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图4" data-mwl-img-id="62217" mwl-index="4"></p><p>6.软件默认安装在C盘，可自定义更改软件安装位置，点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62218 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/6-22.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图5" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图5" data-mwl-img-id="62218" mwl-index="5"></p><p>7.点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62219 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-22.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图6" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图6" data-mwl-img-id="62219" mwl-index="6"></p><p>8.点击【我接受】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62220 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/8-21.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图7" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图7" data-mwl-img-id="62220" mwl-index="7"></p><p>9.点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62221 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-12.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图8" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图8" data-mwl-img-id="62221" mwl-index="8"></p><p>10.点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62222 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/10-11.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图9" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图9" data-mwl-img-id="62222" mwl-index="9"></p><p>11.软件安装中，稍等片刻</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62223 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/11-9.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图10" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图10" data-mwl-img-id="62223" mwl-index="10"></p><p>12.点击【下一步】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62224 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/12-8.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图11" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图11" data-mwl-img-id="62224" mwl-index="11"></p><p>13.点击【完成】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62225 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/13-8.jpg" width="499" height="360" title="Krita 5.2.9插图12" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图12" data-mwl-img-id="62225" mwl-index="12"></p><p>14.回到桌面，右键桌面上的【Krita软件图标】，点击【打开】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62226 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/14-8.jpg" width="328" height="249" title="Krita 5.2.9插图13" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图13" data-mwl-img-id="62226" mwl-index="13"></p><p>15.安装完成</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62227 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-5-1024x649.jpg" width="1024" height="649" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-5-1024x649.jpg 1024w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-5-768x486.jpg 768w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-5-1536x973.jpg 1536w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/15-5.jpg 1939w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" title="Krita 5.2.9插图14" alt="Krita 5.2.9插图14" data-mwl-img-id="62227" mwl-index="14"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
