      <title>PR 2025软件分享安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/26/PR%202025%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/26/PR%202025%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Adobe Premiere Pro 2025 v25.2.0是一款专业的视频编辑软件，在影视制作、广告设计、网络视频创作等领域应用广泛。它支持从8K到虚拟现实等多种现代视频格式，拥有丰富的创意工具和强大的AI功能。如自动创建逐字稿和字幕、清理对话、匹配颜色、智能识别并匹配转场和效果等，能显著减少繁琐工作的时间，提升创作效率。软件还提供专业的音频处理工具，可降低噪音、增强对话，并能利用AI自动配合音乐与剪辑片段。在界面设计上，采用了全新、现代化的设计，提供多种外观模式供用户自定义。此外，Premiere Pro 2025 v25.2.0可与其他Adobe应用程序无缝集成，优化了跨平台协作与云同步功能，借助云端实时共享项目文件，方便团队成员共同编辑和评论。</p><h2>安装教程</h2><p>1.下载完成后，鼠标右击【Premiere 2025 v25.2.0】压缩包，选择【解压至此处】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-62832 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-56.jpg" width="815" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-56.jpg 815w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1-56-768x597.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图" data-mwl-img-id="62832" mwl-index="0"></p><p>2.打开解压后的文件夹，鼠标右击【Set-up】选择【以管理员身份运行】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62833 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-56.jpg" width="815" height="634" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-56.jpg 815w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2-56-768x597.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 815px) 100vw, 815px" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图1" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图1" data-mwl-img-id="62833" mwl-index="1"></p><p>3.点击【Install】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62834 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/3-56.jpg" width="450" height="679" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图2" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图2" data-mwl-img-id="62834" mwl-index="2"></p><p>4.点击【文件夹图标】，点击【更改位置】可以修改软件安装位置，这里我选择默认文件夹，点击【继续】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62835 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/4-56.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图3" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图3" data-mwl-img-id="62835" mwl-index="3"></p><p>5.安装中…</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62836 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/5-55.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图4" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图4" data-mwl-img-id="62836" mwl-index="4"></p><p>6.点击【关闭】</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62837 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/6-54.jpg" width="448" height="677" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图5" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图5" data-mwl-img-id="62837" mwl-index="5"></p><p>7.创建桌面快捷方式：①点击桌面任务栏中的【开始图标】&gt;点击【所有应用】②将【Premiere 2024 v24.1.0】图标拖到电脑桌面</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62838 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-53.jpg" width="817" height="784" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-53.jpg 817w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/7-53-768x737.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图6" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图6" data-mwl-img-id="62838" mwl-index="6"></p><p>8.双击桌面的【Premiere 2024 v24.1.0】图标启动软件</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62839 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/8-52.jpg" width="316" height="236" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图7" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图7" data-mwl-img-id="62839" mwl-index="7"></p><p>9.安装完成</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-62840 mwl-img" src="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-39-1024x492.jpg" width="1024" height="492" srcset="https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-39-1024x492.jpg 1024w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-39-768x369.jpg 768w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-39-1536x739.jpg 1536w, https://www.rjctx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/9-39-2048x985.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" title="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图8" alt="Premiere 2025 v25.2.0插图8" data-mwl-img-id="62840" mwl-index="8"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
